data.description: Welcome to this charming residence nestled in the heart of Arcola! Conveniently located off Highway 6 just a few miles from 288, making an easy commute!  This meticulously maintained 3 bed, 2 bath home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style! The gourmet kitchen serves as the heart of the home, with beautiful granite countertops and gas stove top!  The kitchen opens up to the dining and living area making it perfect for family gatherings and entertaining! Call today to schedule a visit!
